var sCmds = newMenu("SimpleImagesComputing Menu Tool", newArray("Import...", "Ð¡onfigure Parameters Set", "Single Image Treatment", "Export To Excele", "-", "About"));
macro "SimpleImagesComputing Menu Tool - " {
 cmd = getArgument();
 if (cmd=="Import...")
    runMacro("MultiOpenerWizard.txt");
else if (cmd=="Select Parameters Set")
    run ("ParametersSettingWizard.txt");
else if (cmd=="Single Image Treatment")
        runMacro("ImageTreatmentWizard.txt");
else if (cmd=="Export To Excele")
      runMacro("AnalyzerAndXlSaveWizard");
else if (cmd=="About")
      runMacro("About.txt")   ;
}
